01:31.692 --> 01:33.058
Okay, I got some water.

01:39.433 --> 01:40.833
What if we didn't?

01:42.736 --> 01:45.204
Pack it up.

01:45.206 --> 01:49.341
What if we just stayed
forever on this beach?

01:49.343 --> 01:51.176
Cal would not object.

01:52.313 --> 01:53.745
Wait, wait, wait.

01:53.747 --> 01:55.747
