I'm not hungry.

03:26.607 --> 03:28.707
What about you, honey?
You didn't even serve yourself.

03:28.709 --> 03:30.576
- Can I get you...
- No. Thanks. Just...

03:30.578 --> 03:33.312
Truth is, I've been feeling
sick to my stomach all morning.

03:33.314 --> 03:35.714
