a murderer is being released.

03:35.716 --> 03:37.182
- It's...
- Terrifying.

03:37.184 --> 03:38.650
The danger is amping up.

03:38.652 --> 03:40.319
What do you think he's gonna do?

03:40.321 --> 03:43.222
I don't know.

03:43.224 --> 03:47.793
Wolves, peacocks...
It... it... feels like

03:47.795 --> 03:51.763
some kind of answer
has to be in these symbols.

03:51.765 --> 03:53.599
It's right in front of us.

03:56.637 --> 03:57.803
Cal?

04:01.875 --> 04:04.676
What are you doing?!

04:04.678 --> 04:06.745
