04:06.747 --> 04:08.247
What's the matter?

04:08.249 --> 04:10.249
Hey.

04:10.251 --> 04:12.317
Come on, buddy.
We made a deal, right?

04:12.319 --> 04:14.820
You've gotta tell us
what's going on.

04:14.822 --> 04:17.755
I can't.

04:17.757 --> 04:19.423
Cal, please.

04:19.426 --> 04:23.395
Whatever it is,
we will figure it out together.

04:23.397 --> 04:24.796
I can only tell Zeke.

